[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1328","title":"Red Hat Linux linuxconf 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中 linuxconf 工具在 1.11.r11-rh3 之前版本存在安全漏洞，本地用户可通过符号链接攻击（symlink attack）覆盖任意系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1328"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至 1.11.r11-rh3 或更高版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。Red Hat 官方已发布 RH51 安全公告提供更新包，建议用户通过 Red Hat 官方渠道获取并安装补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:21:58.102130741+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90383955231511&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7232.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6068","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#linuxconf"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 及 OpenBSD 等 BSD 衍生系统 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20），远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统内核崩溃或死锁，进而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至修复版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 或 3.0 及以上版本，OpenBSD 升级至 2.4 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可在边界防火墙上过滤畸形 IP 分片包，或禁用不必要的 raw socket 处理功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 实现拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BSD 衍生系统（包括 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等）的 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证漏洞（CWE-20），未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"立即将 FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或将 OpenBSD 升级至 2.3 及以上版本；对于无法升级的系统，下载并安装对应厂商发布的 ip_input.c 补丁。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，丢弃入站 IP 分片包（若业务不需要分片功能），或部署支持 IP 分片校验的入侵防御系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0455","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Expression Evaluator 远程文件读取删除漏洞","description":"ColdFusion 的 Expression Evaluator 示例应用（exprcalc.cfm）存在未授权访问漏洞，由于未对服务器资源访问进行适当限制，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问该示例页面读取或删除服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Adobe ColdFusion 服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0455"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.050","remediation":"删除或移除 ColdFusion 服务器上的 `exprcalc.cfm` 及整个 `/cfdocs/` 示例应用目录；升级到 Adobe 官方仍在维护的 ColdFusion (2021/2023) 最新版本；在 Web 服务器层（IIS/Apache/Nginx）通过访问控制规则禁止外部访问 `/CFIDE/` 和 `/cfdocs/` 目录，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0200","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0477","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 远程文件上传与执行漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0 的 Expression Evaluator 组件中 openfile.cfm 文件未对远程用户的文件操作进行有效权限限制，导致存在访问控制缺陷。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向服务器上传任意文件，进而实现文件显示、删除或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 ColdFusion Server 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0477"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.877","remediation":"升级到 Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0.1 或更高版本，或移除/限制对 openfile.cfm 的匿名访问权限，通过 Web 服务器配置（如 IIS 或 Apache）禁止外部直接访问该文件。如无法升级，可在应用层实现对 openfile.cfm 的 IP 白名单访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0892","title":"Netscape Communicator 动态字体处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.7 之前版本在处理动态字体时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可构造一个长度字段值小于字体实际尺寸的恶意字体文件，诱使用户通过受影响浏览器访问包含该字体的网页，触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Netscape Communicator 浏览器系列，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0892"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.440","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7 或更高版本，该版本修复了动态字体解析中的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法升级，可在浏览器设置中禁用动态字体渲染功能，并考虑迁移至仍在维护的替代浏览器以减少风险暴露。通过防火墙阻断外部字体服务器连接也可作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0892"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0949","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1109","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.10.0 ETRN命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.10.0 之前版本中存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 SMTP 服务器发送大量 ETRN 命令后立即断开连接来触发该漏洞。当攻击者断开连接后，Sendmail 进程仍会继续处理已接收的 ETRN 命令，持续消耗服务器资源，导致邮件服务响应缓慢甚至崩溃，影响正常邮件收发功能。该漏洞利用简单，无需认证，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1109"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.347","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.10.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ETRN 命令处理中连接断开后继续处理导致资源耗尽的问题。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制 ETRN 命令来源 IP，或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口入站连接频次作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94632241202626&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780566911948&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7760.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/904","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19701","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/sendmail_etrn_dos.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000955.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1109.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0919","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0919.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1066","title":"id Software Quake 1 服务器 UDP 反射放大漏洞","description":"id Software Quake 1 服务器在处理 UDP 游戏连接初始请求时存在流量放大缺陷。攻击者可伪造源 IP 地址向目标 Quake 1 服务器发送特制的初始连接请求包，服务器会向该伪造的源地址（即受害者）返回大量响应流量，从而导致反射型放大攻击。此漏洞与 Smurf 攻击类似，允许远程攻击者利用第三方 Quake 1 服务器作为放大器对目标主机实施分布式拒绝服务攻击（DDoS），攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，影响所有使用 id Software Quake 1 服务器软件的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1066"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Quake 1 官方最新补丁或改用现代分支服务端（如 ezQuake、QuakeSpasm 等），这些版本已修复 UDP 流量放大问题。在网络层面启用 uRPF（单播反向路径转发）过滤源地址欺骗包，并在防火墙限制目标 UDP 端口 26000-27000 的入站速率，防止被用于放大攻击。如不再需要对外提供游戏服务，建议直接在防火墙层面禁用该端口的公网映射。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94589559631535&w=2","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1066"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0919.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1682","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0997","title":"WU-FTPD FTP Conversion 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2至2.6.2版本中启用了FTP文件转换功能时存在命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过上传包含特殊畸形文件名的文件，该文件名在传输过程中被作为参数传递给转换程序（如tar或uncompress），从而导致任意命令在服务器端执行。该漏洞影响多版本WU-FTPD服务器，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高危。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需具备FTP上传权限即可触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0997"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.343","remediation":"升级至 wu-ftpd 2.6.3 或更高版本以修复此漏洞；若无法升级，在 ftpaccess 配置文件中关闭 conversion 功能，注释或移除相关 conversion 规则，并限制匿名用户上传目录不可执行转换操作。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 tar、uncompress 等转换程序的 setuid 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-377","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20563","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0997","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0997.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/wu_ftpd_site_exec.nasl","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/debian_DSA-377.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0850","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1005","title":"Novell GroupWise GWWEB.EXE 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Novell GroupWise 邮件系统的 Web 服务器组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在目录遍历漏洞。由于对 HELP 参数输入过滤不严，远程攻击者无需身份认证，可通过包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求绕过路径限制，读取服务器上任意 .htm 扩展名的文件，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 GroupWise 5.2 及 5.5 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1005"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.380","remediation":"升级 Novell GroupWise 至 5.5 Enhancement Pack 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 或 Netscape Enterprise Server）上通过 ACL 限制对 GWWEB.EXE 的访问，或删除该 CGI 文件。若无需 Web 邮件功能，建议禁用整个 CGI-BIN/GW5 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/3413","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/879","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19682","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1005","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1005.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1005.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjwc-hc6j-xvf2/GHSA-wjwc-hc6j-xvf2.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1005.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0850.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0852","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1006","title":"Novell GroupWise Web服务器路径遍历漏洞","description":"Novell Groupwise 的 Web 服务器组件 GWWEB.EXE 存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HELP 参数提交特制的路径遍历请求，导致服务器返回文件系统路径信息，从而泄露 Web 服务器的真实安装目录路径。该漏洞可被用于后续攻击步骤的信息收集阶段，帮助攻击者进一步探测目标系统，扩大攻击面。受影响版本为 Novell Groupwise 5.5 及可能更早版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1006"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.503","remediation":"升级 Novell GroupWise 至 6.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 GWWEB.EXE 路径泄露问题。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中移除或禁用 GWWEB.EXE 的 CGI 映射，并限制对 /cgi-bin/GW5/GWWEB.EXE 的访问权限以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94571433731824&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1006","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1006.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1006.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q/GHSA-j6r8-2wq6-f58q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/groupwise_web_interface_help_hole.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88366/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1006.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0852.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0826","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0994","title":"Microsoft Windows NT SYSKEY 密码哈希加密密钥流重用漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中 SYSKEY 机制存在密钥流重用漏洞。SYSKEY 用于加密 SAM 数据库中的密码哈希，但由于其在加密过程中重复使用相同的密钥流，攻击者可通过分析多个加密后的密码哈希值，利用密钥流重用特性还原出明文密码。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，本地攻击者需具备系统访问权限，可通过暴力破解或差分分析手段获取用户凭据，导致系统账户安全受到威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0994"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.960","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本且无官方补丁。建议立即升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本操作系统，并启用 Kerberos 认证替代 NTLM；对于仍在使用 NT 的环境，应使用 SYSKEY 的增强模式（Syskey.exe /E）强制使用密码保护，并在注册表 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa` 中设置 `NoLMHash=1` 禁用 LM Hash 存储以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248183","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/873","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-056","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0994","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0994.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94/GHSA-r7rj-gr4g-8x94.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0994.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0826.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0830","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0998","title":"思科缓存引擎缓存内容替换漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎（Cisco Cache Engine）存在缓存内容替换漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向缓存引擎发送恶意请求，替换或污染缓存中的合法内容，导致后续用户访问时被重定向至恶意资源或获取被篡改的数据。该漏洞源于缓存引擎对内容更新缺乏充分的访问控制与校验机制，影响使用思科缓存引擎的网络环境。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0998"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.483","remediation":"将 Cisco Cache Engine 软件升级至版本 3.2.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了缓存内容替换漏洞。若无法升级，可在网络边界配置 ACL，限制仅信任源访问 Cache Engine 的管理接口（TCP 80）和代理端口（TCP 3128/8080），并禁用不必要的远程管理功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0998","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0998.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0998.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87024/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0830.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0833","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1000","title":"Cisco Cache Engine Web管理界面信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco Cache Engine 的 Web 管理界面存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接访问性能统计页面，获取系统运行状态、网络流量、缓存命中率及客户端连接等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Cisco Cache Engine 系列设备，攻击者可利用泄露的数据分析网络拓扑与流量模式，为后续攻击收集情报，需通过访问控制限制管理接口的访问范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1000"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.750","remediation":"在 Cache Engine 上配置访问控制列表 (ACL)，仅允许特定管理 IP 访问 Web 管理界面（如 `access-list 10 permit 192.168.0.0 0.0.0.255` 后在 HTTP 配置中引用）。建议将管理口绑定到独立 management VLAN，避免与业务网络互通。如无需远程 Web 管理，在 CLI 下执行 `no ip http server` 关闭 HTTP 服务。由于 Cisco Cache Engine 已全面停产停服，建议迁移至 Cisco WAAS 或等效替代产品以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1000","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1000.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445/GHSA-6xm7-wpgr-j445.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1000.json","https://github.com/GiovanniMenon/llm4cve/blob/3ca85b2ae823c06810c546f320c2cd2f2707043f/README.md","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87010/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0833.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0833.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0837","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0837.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1001","title":"Cisco 缓存引擎访问验证漏洞","description":"思科缓存引擎存在访问验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过提交空用户名和密码绕过身份认证机制，未经授权访问系统管理接口或敏感配置信息。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Cisco Cache Engine 设备，攻击者无需任何凭证即可利用此漏洞，导致设备管理权限遭非法获取。CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，建议升级到不受影响版本或配置访问控制列表加以缓解。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1001"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.860","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Cisco 替代产品